element.name: HIVInfo 4.0
element.documentation: VAAC requirement: HIV Info 4.0 is the main system for storage of case reporting data - we enhance it to make it support international standards

node.label: From here on, the systems proposed are open-source, easy to use and maintain, because they have a large support community, they are based on industry standard technologies, and it's part of the PATH program to enable teams to support and develop these tools.
We should clarify the roles (data repository and Web UI) between HIVInfo 4.0 and HAPI
Source code repositories should be made available
